Title: Implement display options for all visuals (-> PNP timeranges)
Component: multisite
State: open
Date: 2014-07-15 11:59:08
Targetversion: 1.2.5i1
Class: feature

At the moment the pnp timerange is configured e.g. for the dashlet within the dashlet
itselfs. It would be better to generalize this to use the generic PNP timerange display
option which is used within the views.

To make this possible the visuals code needs to implement the display options.
